videos.headline: Iowa gets lucky bounce for interception
videos.description: Iowa's Desmond King comes up with a big interception when the ball bounces off his body and he is able to corral it.

videos.headline: Iowa TE stays in bounds with juggling catch
videos.description: Iowa TE Peter Pekar gets both feet in bounds and makes the tough catch.

videos.headline: Florida makes goal-line stand
videos.description: Florida's Marcell Harris gets into the backfield and stops Iowa's LeShun Daniels on fourth down.

videos.headline: Florida's Thompson slips past Iowa for 85-yard TD
videos.description: Florida RB Mark Thompson receives a screen pass and breaks through an array of tackles before racing 85 yards downfield for the touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Florida's Thompson slips past Iowa for 85-yard TD) 2017/01/02

videos.headline: Iowa fights for first down on third-and-15
videos.description: Iowa's Akrum Wadley catches the screen pass and breaks a few tackles for a first down.

videos.headline: Florida extends its lead
videos.description: Austin Appleby finds a wide open DeAndre Goolsby for the touchdown.

videos.headline: Florida DB Gardner turns interception into touchdown
videos.description: Chauncey Gardner picks off Iowa and runs 58 yards for the touchdown.

videos.headline: Florida's Gardner gets his second interception of the game
videos.description: Iowa's offense continues to struggle as Florida DB Chauncey Gardner intercepts C.J. Beathard for the second time.

videos.headline: Florida picks off Iowa's Beathard for the third time
videos.description: Daniel McMillian gets Florida's third interception off of C.J. Beathard.
